25
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,639
Of course they can't.

26
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,240
But Mei Lin,

27
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:20,240
take one step forward,

28
00:02:20,879 --> 00:02:22,520
and I'll kill ten of them.

29
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,560
Take two steps,

30
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:27,439
and I'll kill 100.

31
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,599
